free:
Shows how much memory (RAM) is used and how much is free.
Helps in checking memory status.
Syntax: free

vmstat:
It display the system performance details like memory and CPU usage and process status.
Useful for finding performance issues.
Syntax: vmstat

ping:
Ping(packet internet groper)it is used to checks the network connectivity b/n host and a server
It sends a signal to another computer and waits for a reply.
Also shows how fast the connection is.
Syntax: ping [options] destination
Example: ping google.com


cat:
Used to show the content of a file on the screen.
It is also used to create or join multiple files.
Syntax: cat filename